title: The giant free music topic.
content:
Yes, it exists music made by bands who let you download it for free. For promotion of their new albums for example or just for the fun.
So this topic is to place your links of good bands who have some free songs to download so other Keeners can listen to them and discuss them.
PLEASE ONLY FULL SONGS FROM PROFESSIONAL BANDS AND NO SAMPLES!

What I got:

Therion, a symphonic/orchestral heavy metal band has made three nice cover available for download:
[url=http://storage.megatherion.com/mp3/therion-judaspriest-gm.mp3]Judas Priest - The Green Manalishi [/url]
[url=http://storage.megatherion.com/mp3/therion-metallica-ffwf.mp3]Metallica - Figh fire with fire[/url]
[url=http://storage.megatherion.com/mp3/therion-thinlizzy-southbound.mp3]Thin Lizzy - Southbound[/url]

Judas Priest one of the most famous heavy metal bands new singe:
[url=http://www.synvinkel.net/Music/Revolution.mp3]Revolution[/url]

System of a Downs new song:
